* EDA

---

# IMPORTANT THEORY

# Data Visualization

Graphical representation of data.

---

# EDA

Exploratory Data Analysis.

---

# Histogram

Shows frequency distribution.

---

# Countplot

Shows categorical counts.

---

# Hue

Separates graph by categories.

